============================
eZ Recommendation Service
============================

Description
-----------
The eZ Recommendation Service provided by YOOCHOOSE represents your first
opportunity to customize and personalize your online portal individually for
each end user. News, images, videos and events are recommended in
real time depending on the users' consumption behaviour and the content.


Requirements
------------

- eZ Publish version 4.6 or newer
- The PECL HTTP extension: http://fr.php.net/http

License
-------
The license of this extension can be found in the LICENSE file.

Installation
-----------
The installation procedure is described in the INSTALL file.